      <p>A <a href="ch72s04.html#MonstersT-Z21">titan</a> is about 25 feet tall and weighs about 14,000 pounds.<a href="img/MonstersT-Z.Titan.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersT-Z.Titan.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p><a href="ch72s04.html#MonstersT-Z21">Titans</a> speak Abyssal, Common, Celestial, Draconic, and <a href="ch66s06.html#MonstersG67">Giant</a>.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
